msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/wererat.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Shapechanger.** The wererat can use its action to polymorph into a "
"rat-humanoid hybrid or into a giant rat, or back into its true form, which "
"is humanoid. Its statistics, other than its size, are the same in each "
"form. Any equipment it is wearing or carrying isn't transformed. It reverts "
"to its true form if it dies.    \n"
"**Keen Smell.** The wererat has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that "
"rely on smell. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/wererat.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack (Humanoid or Hybrid Form Only).** The wererat makes two "
"attacks, only one of which can be a bite.    \n"
"**Bite (Rat or Hybrid Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach "
"5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 4 (1d4 + 2) piercing damage. If the target is a "
"humanoid, it must succeed on a DC 11 Constitution saving throw or be cursed "
"with wererat lycanthropy.    \n"
"**Shortsword (Humanoid or Hybrid Form Only).** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to "
"hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Hand Crossbow (Humanoid or Hybrid Form Only).** _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +4 "
"to hit, range 30/120 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.\n"
msgstr ""
